    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Gem cut in the shape of a square with rounded corners and small facets on the top (table). A gem cut in the shape of a cushion is often compared to the princess cut because of their square appearance.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
